pathy and a sprinkling of good taste and you have the perfect recipe for winning products.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"skills\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-337\" title=\"playtimeicon-01\" src=\"http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/micah-icons-01.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"125\" height=\"126\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Direction</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Building products and creating in teams is all about a conversation of what is possible. I curate and empower designers and project managers to push through creative boundaries under the constraint of tight timelines. Direction is about leading the way but moving forward together.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"skills\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-336\" title=\"playtimeicon-04\" src=\"http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/micah-icons-04.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"125\" height=\"126\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Playtime</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">As Director and Co-Founder of Playtime Collective, I lead a fearless force of talented designers, skillful makers, focused nerds, and insightful visionaries. Our whole team approaches each project with a sharp focus on innovation to create and consult on unique culture building products.</p>\r\n<a title=\"Playtime Collective\" href=\"http://www.playtimecollective.com\" target=\"_blank\"> &gt; Our Site</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"float: left; width: 75px; padding-right: 40px; margin-left: 135px;\">\r\n<h3>Realms</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"float: left; width: 600px;\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 150px;\"><em>Health Service Strategy and Innovation, Financial Services, Home Service/Product Invention, Mobile Service Strategy, Youth Behaviors, Visual Communication, Learning, Play, Retail Expereince, Creative Power, Sustainable Living </em></p>\r\n\r\n</div>','Expertise','','pu