he countryside where I climbed trees and played in the woods. From a young age I was blowing glass, painting canvases, shooting travel photography, and making things. I’ve put these passions to work at Art School, Design School, and Business School where I focused on Service Design and Environmental Studies.\r\n\r\nI’ve experimented with different strategies of identifying and realizing scalable and high impact products on my own and in teams working closely with others. I’ve consulted for <strong>Louis Vuitton</strong> on luxury marketing strategy and service design, <strong>Memorial Sloan Kettering</strong> on Health Service Innovation for chemotherapy patients and <strong>First Niagara Bank</strong> on Gen-Y strategy. I’ve recently consulted with <strong>MTV </strong>and was a panelist invited by <strong>WHATIF</strong> for a study on Gen-Y trends. I have traveled the world extensively (my passport is almost full), I’m a pro at Where’s Waldo and I can be very competitive on the foose-ball table!\r\n\r\nEducation: Maryland Institute College of Art, Yestermerrow Design Build School, Eugene Lang the New School for Liberal Arts, Parsons the New School for Design, Columbia Business School','About','','inherit','open','open','','4-revision-79','','','2012-05-26 16:53:09','2012-05-26 20:53:09','',4,'http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/?p=411',0,'revision','',0),(22,1,'2012-05-06 21:15:59','2012-05-06 21:15:59','[recent_projects num=\"6\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThis is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This is some text. This 