at is Uberpay.me. The best way to send and receive money with a text or an email.\n\nIn the future when the user reaches the account fund limit they are introduced to First Niagara\'s Savings accounts. Now that your Gen Y customer is comfortable with your App, they are now ready to get serious and commit a bit more. It\'s super easy now too because the bank already has all of their important information. Just click a button online to add a savings account and customers can start transferring money from your UberPay.me account instantly and free.\n\n&nbsp;','UberPay.me, First Niagara Bank','','inherit','open','open','','47-autosave','','','2012-05-28 22:49:58','2012-05-29 02:49:58','',47,'http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/?p=80',0,'revision','',0),(63,1,'2012-05-10 04:10:22','2012-05-10 04:10:22','','cargocollective-3','','inherit','open','open','','cargocollective-3','','','2012-05-10 04:10:22','2012-05-10 04:10:22','',53,'http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/cargocollective-3.png',2,'attachment','image/png',0),(64,1,'2012-05-10 04:01:32','2012-05-10 04:01:32','[infos phone=\"<a href=\"tel:860.485.2099\" target=\"_blank\">860.485.2099</a>\" email=\"micah@micahspear.com\"]\r\n\r\n[contact_form to=\"micah@micahspear.com\"]','Contact','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-3','','','2012-05-10 04:01:32','2012-05-10 04:01:32','',10,'http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/?p=64',0,'revision','',0),(68,1,'2012-05-10 04:43:05','2012-05-10 04:43:05','[skills]\r\n[skill value=\"100\" color=\"red\" text=\"Photoshop\"] [skill value=\"80\" color=\"yellow\" text=\"Illustrator\"] [skill value=\"90\" color=\"blue\" text=\"HTML/CSS\"] [skill value=\"65\" color=\"gray\" text=\"JavaScript\"]\r\n[skill value=\"45\" color=\"green\" text=\"WordPress\"] [skill value=\"35\" color=\"brown\" text=\"PHP/mySQL\"] [/skills]','Services','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-3','','','2012-05-10 04:43:05','2012-05-10 04:43:05','',8,'ht