sight</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">How do you identify an “aha moment”? Think about it for a second. Design gaps and revealing opportunities can appear out of thin air. It takes keen awareness and finely tuned listening to realize the hidden nature of things. Ask questions first, design later.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"skills\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-334\" title=\"playtimeicon-02\" src=\"http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/micah-icons-02.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"125\" height=\"126\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Innovation</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Effective, innovative ideas require disruptive thinking and intuition. Leverage these assets with an understanding and appreciation of our social/technological evolution, and you have a recipe for winning products.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"skills\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-337\" title=\"playtimeicon-01\" src=\"http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/micah-icons-01.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"125\" height=\"126\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Direction</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For me building products and creating in teams is all about the back and forth conversation of what is possible. I curate and empower designers and project managers to push through creative boundaries under tight timelines. Direction is about leading the way, together.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"skills\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-336\" title=\"playtimeicon-04\" src=\"http://ec2-50-17-60-123.compute-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/micah-icons-04.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"125\" height=\"126\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Playtime</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">As Director and Co-Founder of Playtime Collective, I lead a force of designers, makers, nerds, and visionaries. Our team approaches each project with the insight and innova